ler-Lissner SA "Adverse effects of laxatives: fact and fiction." Pharmacology 47 (1993): 138-45[5] Canadian Pharmacists Association "e-CPS. Available from: URL: http://www.pharmacists.ca/function/Subscriptions/ecps.cfm?link=eCPS_quikLink."[6] Chin RL "Laxative-induced hypokalemia." Ann Emerg Med 32 (1998): 517-8', 1767369485);
